aim_sniper_race
Created By Naticus 3/28/2010
http://www.jgcclan.net/

Intro:
=======
This is a sniper racing map.  Shoot the targets at each station to open the door to the next area to score one kill each.
Finishing the course first will score you 3 kills plus eliminate the other side! Don't miss with the AWP 
or it will mean a time consuming reload.   

Footnote:
=========
Thanks to Swampy Turtle for a great idea and to the JGC Clan for their support.

Have fun !

[video de présentation ! Introduce video](http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GdMCYphAgq8&feature=youtu.be "http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GdMCYphAgq8&feature=youtu.be")

Notes
 This map does not come with a nav file. I will either include this in an update or next release, or not include it at all.

make of the classic aim_sniperYard, this version is source-ified,and winter-ized. Some familiar players may recognize some original features, Such as the idle truck. You may also note some new features, such as new hallways and a new staircase. Either way, enjoy the map. If you have any problems, contact me, and I'll see to getting an update to fix any problems one may encounter. I have already recieved reports of the map crashing servers. I have not confirmed this. I do know that this map does not crash while playing offline. I can not identify the problem at this time.

_sText: This is the first map I actually published. Its not big, its made for improving your skill or just for playing with your friends for fun. It took me nearly half a day to make it, with all the lighting, details and messing around with textures so they don't look looped, because some of them do (by looping I mean you can see that in ends in the middle and its the same thing in squares). Hope you like it, or I'm not sure if you should, it's my first "successful map" I made I could say. It might look familiar to $2000$, because there's from I got my inspiration. Please don't hate about it just because it's my first map doesn't mean I cannot improve. Btw bots on normal are dominating me in this map for some reason. There are some easter eggs but most of them wont be able to be found without noclip. I'll let you find out what's in this map. Anyways, tell me what maps or ideas what I can do or maybe how can I improve it and what should I not do and fix something in this map, I'll try to. Happy frags.
